&lt;p&gt;Are you a looking for an exciting new opportunity? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you have experience handling telephone and face to face requests?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience of working in a GP Practice?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Customer care experience is an essential as well as basic word, excel and email skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If this sounds like you, Broad Oak Medical Practice are looking for a receptionist for up to 25 hours per week, to work between the hours of 8am – 8pm Monday and 8am – 6.30pm Tues - Friday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please contact recruitment@operosehealth.co.uk&lt;/p&gt;
